author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Once (Twice... Thrice...) again a great delivery... :_ちょうちょ:
(And personally talking, finally celebrating the 800000 subs)

Well... This time was short, but also passionated utawaku.
Really Rushia is great at singing, not only at high notes, also low notes. :_るんるん:
At singing "Mononoke-hime", I was starting to fall asleep due to her relaxing voice. 😌💤 (This is also because there are 12 hour difference between Japan and where I live, at that hour I would be sleeping, but with wanting to watch Rushia-daitenshi...)

And at Supaachaato Orei Time, it was raining game recommendations... Various fans at LiveChat were recommendating APEX, but Rushia had a not good experience at First Person Shooter games.
Someone said, inside Hololive... Matsuri-san, Botan-chan and Towa-chan are accurated.
I was thinking in someone outside Hololive, a "half twin sister" who was APEX tournament's champion about few days ago.
(Rushia's half Twin sister, because her designer is the same Yasuyuki-sensei) 
Well, forget my idea...

2:52:40, talking about videogame recommendations... One of them was sent via Naisupa already read by Rushia... Videogame's name is "Yakiniku Bugyou" (焼肉奉行), it's a Puzzle videogame, also a cooking videogame, totally accurated. :_きゅん:

2:42:07 "Lasagna Beam" (I'm hungry) :_ハート:
